				</fill>
			</Rect>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="66" y="858" width="504" height="135" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">由守望者大招召唤，每个元素星的生命值为守望者的<span color="#ffdfbf">1/6</span><span>；<br/>活性元素星免疫对应属性伤害；惰性岩元素星全抗</span><span color="#ffdfbf">80%</span><span>;<br/>破坏第</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2</span><span>颗元素星将对守望者造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2段3%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2段9%生命值</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffffbf">对应元素真伤</span><span>(仅暴击的一段有附着)。<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">(N4) </span><span>惰性岩元素星全抗提升至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">140%</span><span>;<br/></span><span color="#bfffbf">(N4) </span><span>若守望者召唤了两枚不同的元素星，则它们的生命值将降至守望者的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1/15</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="698" width="508" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">大招之前会施放2次，每次会分别记录<span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span>的攻击次数，首次施放时，当某一元素次数达</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3次</span><span>时，即为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">记录完成</span><span>，并作为元素星的属性储存，记录时间为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5s</span><span>；若第二次记录的元素与首次</span><span color="#ffdfbf">相同</span><span>，则需要</span><span color="#ffdfbf">9次攻击</span><span>才能被记录。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span><span> 整个技能期间的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">全抗+70%</span><span>，且两次记录的次数需求提升至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5次</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15次</span><span>；进入第二次记录的间隔大幅缩短，第二次的记录时间延长至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">8s</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/啸卷之役-开眼者%B7傲然睥睨.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1166" y="847" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
